<item>
            <title>[LU-17134] Is IML monitoring package compatible with Lustre 2.15.X?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17134</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&apos;re currently running a Lustre setup on version 2.15.2 with RHEL8 as OS. Could you confirm if the IML monitoring package, available at this GitHub link ( &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/whamcloud/integrated-manager-for-lustre&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/whamcloud/integrated-manager-for-lustre&lt;/a&gt;), is compatible with the Lustre 2.15.X series?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, could you recommend any other efficient monitoring tools? While we have Barreleye Monitoring, lustre_exporter, node_exporter, and LOKI for monitoring, we&apos;re open to have other options.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Jane&lt;/p&gt;</description>
